1
00:00:08,660 --> 00:00:09,219
Look.

2
00:00:10,579 --> 00:00:12,260
Yours looks better.

3
00:00:12,819 --> 00:00:13,728
Mine looks good, huh?

4
00:00:14,299 --> 00:00:15,539
I tried to talk you out of it,

5
00:00:15,539 --> 00:00:16,859
but you insisted on this one.

6
00:00:17,379 --> 00:00:18,379
Regretting it now.

7
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:21,660
I'm always like this.

8
00:00:21,940 --> 00:00:23,060
Never hold onto the best.

9
00:00:25,420 --> 00:00:26,659
It's okay.

10
00:00:26,779 --> 00:00:28,220
Just a manicure.

11
00:00:29,019 --> 00:00:30,220
At worst, remove and redo it.

12
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:31,619
I'll go with you.

13
00:00:34,659 --> 00:00:35,580
So good to have you,

14
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:36,339
Ruoxi.

15
00:00:37,619 --> 00:00:38,500
What?

16
00:00:38,780 --> 00:00:39,860
Why so serious?

17
00:00:43,540 --> 00:00:44,379
What's wrong?

18
00:00:45,379 --> 00:00:46,820
Did something happen?

19
00:00:51,059 --> 00:00:52,180
Alright.

20
00:00:52,419 --> 00:00:53,860
Let me tell you some good news.

21
00:00:54,739 --> 00:00:55,860
He promised me.

22
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:59,180
He promised you?

23
00:01:02,739 --> 00:01:05,260
To leave Deep In The Bustle
and live an ordinary life with you?

24
00:01:11,060 --> 00:01:12,739
But regarding Feng,

25
00:01:13,420 --> 00:01:15,140
he's still a bit worried.

26
00:01:15,459 --> 00:01:16,620
He'll figure something out.

27
00:01:23,539 --> 00:01:24,659
Let me show you this.

28
00:01:24,819 --> 00:01:25,659
What is this?

29
00:01:27,739 --> 00:01:28,780
Well.

30
00:01:29,019 --> 00:01:30,980
I planned one for you, one for me,

31
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:32,620
so we could make two necklaces later.

32
00:01:33,659 --> 00:01:35,819
Now that I see how happy
you are with Mr. Tu,

33
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:37,140
I'll step aside.

34
00:01:38,259 --> 00:01:39,140
Here, press it.

35
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:40,220
I'll make you a necklace.

36
00:01:42,179 --> 00:01:44,420
You're a bit jealous?

37
00:01:45,580 --> 00:01:46,420
Let's do it together.

38
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,459
He's just a man.

39
00:01:48,620 --> 00:01:50,459
Doesn't know about female bonding.

40
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:52,220
I'll go first.

41
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:55,379
Done.

42
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:40,384
=The Glory Fades=

43
00:02:40,384 --> 00:02:43,008
=Episode 33=
(Truth and Lies)

44
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:46,139
I want to hear it from you directly.

45
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,979
Did you kill An Ruoxi?

46
00:02:49,419 --> 00:02:50,220
Yes.

47
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:53,780
Why?

48
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,940
Because she wanted too much.

49
00:02:56,699 --> 00:02:58,976
Because she became
an obstacle for the Grand Princess.

50
00:02:59,699 --> 00:03:02,379
Tu Jiasheng could never leave
Deep In The Bustle.

51
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,800
Yet she stubbornly tried to change it

52
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,979
using her own strength.

53
00:03:07,539 --> 00:03:09,180
Then the only result is her death.

54
00:03:13,859 --> 00:03:14,740
Meng Yin,

55
00:03:15,859 --> 00:03:17,060
I never thought

56
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,419
it would be you.

57
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,659
I never imagined

58
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:24,379
you served the Grand Princess.

59
00:03:27,659 --> 00:03:28,460
Ruoxi,

60
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,340
I was sent to Deep In The Bustle

61
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,340
to watch Tu Jiasheng

62
00:03:36,539 --> 00:03:37,952
to sever his tie with young lady.

63
00:03:41,379 --> 00:03:42,940
After you appeared,

64
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:49,300
seemed he might keep his promise.

65
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:51,900
I never expected

66
00:03:53,539 --> 00:03:55,259
that I was merely Tu Jiasheng's

67
00:03:56,139 --> 00:03:58,180
tool to appease the Grand Princess.

68
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:12,979
The second time
he begged the Grand Princess

69
00:04:14,379 --> 00:04:16,180
was for Nie Feng's father 's case.

70
00:04:17,579 --> 00:04:19,379
The Grand Princess set one condition:

71
00:04:20,579 --> 00:04:22,860
He had to work for her from then on.

72
00:04:24,779 --> 00:04:28,060
How dare you try to influence him
at such a time

73
00:04:29,339 --> 00:04:30,500
to betray the Grand Princess?

74
00:04:34,579 --> 00:04:35,379
Betrayal

75
00:04:37,259 --> 00:04:38,899
is not permitted.

76
00:04:40,899 --> 00:04:41,980
I never intended

77
00:04:43,379 --> 00:04:45,500
to disrupt the Grand Princess' plans.

78
00:04:46,379 --> 00:04:47,379
I just

79
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,899
wanted him

80
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:53,060
to commit fewer evil deeds

81
00:04:54,019 --> 00:04:55,500
and live with me

82
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:58,540
a simple, ordinary life.

83
00:04:59,819 --> 00:05:00,819
How naive.

84
00:05:01,259 --> 00:05:03,180
How utterly naive you are!

85
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:07,779
Has he ever done fewer evil deeds?

86
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,300
To climb the ladder,

87
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,860
he has done any dirty deed back then.

88
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,779
You just don't know

89
00:05:12,779 --> 00:05:14,699
how many lives he has taken.

90
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,620
You think refusing a few deals

91
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:19,660
for the Grand Princess

92
00:05:20,219 --> 00:05:22,060
will spare him a few levels in hell?

93
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:26,779
No way, listen, An Ruoxi!

94
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,259
You're too naive.

95
00:05:32,259 --> 00:05:33,899
He built Deep In The Bustle.

96
00:05:35,379 --> 00:05:37,819
He can't just abandon it
for a simple life with you.

97
00:05:37,819 --> 00:05:38,980
Don't you understand?

98
00:05:44,779 --> 00:05:45,940
I understand now.

99
00:05:48,019 --> 00:05:49,259
But it's too late.

100
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:51,860
Right?

101
00:05:58,339 --> 00:06:00,300
I fall in love with Tu Jiasheng,

102
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,579
but I don't regret it.

103
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:06,300
Whether I'm a tool,

104
00:06:07,379 --> 00:06:08,379
a puppet

105
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:12,219
or just a passerby in his life,

106
00:06:14,779 --> 00:06:16,339
it doesn't matter.

107
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:18,579
After all,

108
00:06:19,779 --> 00:06:21,100
love is beautiful.

109
00:06:23,139 --> 00:06:24,259
Meng Yin,

110
00:06:25,420 --> 00:06:26,819
you've never loved.

111
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,100
You wouldn't understand.

112
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:33,339
I've never loved?

113
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,819
Is the person you love

114
00:06:39,579 --> 00:06:41,620
worth dying for?

115
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,259
Ruoxi,

116
00:06:51,019 --> 00:06:52,540
if you weren't you,

117
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:54,500
and I weren't me,

118
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,420
we'd surely have more time.

119
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:11,139
Meng Yin,

120
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:13,860
I don't blame you.

121
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:18,100
But you know

122
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,139
I have a sister.

123
00:07:22,339 --> 00:07:24,019
She might track you down.

124
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:28,699
Promise me.

125
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,300
Protect her.

126
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,259
Okay?

127
00:08:54,036 --> 00:08:55,276
Pah!

128
00:08:56,557 --> 00:08:57,396
Meng Yin,

129
00:08:58,396 --> 00:08:59,957
Tu Jiasheng used Ruoxi.

130
00:09:00,597 --> 00:09:02,197
What did that have to do with her?

131
00:09:03,357 --> 00:09:04,876
I was truly blind.

132
00:09:05,516 --> 00:09:06,676
Ruoxi was blind too

133
00:09:06,676 --> 00:09:08,437
to be friends with someone like you.

134
00:09:08,477 --> 00:09:09,676
I promised Ruoxi

135
00:09:09,876 --> 00:09:10,996
to protect you.

136
00:09:11,396 --> 00:09:12,557
But if you still investigate,

137
00:09:12,557 --> 00:09:13,597
you'll end up like her.

138
00:09:13,597 --> 00:09:14,477
Understand?

139
00:09:15,357 --> 00:09:16,077
No need.

140
00:09:16,876 --> 00:09:17,876
Just kill me.

141
00:09:18,796 --> 00:09:19,597
Meng Yin,

142
00:09:20,237 --> 00:09:21,796
you're pathetic.

143
00:09:22,396 --> 00:09:23,796
No one loves you.

144
00:09:24,756 --> 00:09:25,916
In this world,

145
00:09:26,237 --> 00:09:27,837
you only live for yourself.

146
00:09:28,276 --> 00:09:29,237
Su Yunian,

147
00:09:29,357 --> 00:09:30,477
I'll say it again.

148
00:09:30,477 --> 00:09:32,197
Ruoxi asked me to protect you.

149
00:09:32,876 --> 00:09:34,156
Protect me?

150
00:09:34,516 --> 00:09:36,597
Have a murderer protect me?

151
00:09:36,597 --> 00:09:37,676
Ridiculous.

152
00:09:37,856 --> 00:09:38,676
Believe it or not.

153
00:09:38,676 --> 00:09:39,396
Kill me.

154
00:09:39,636 --> 00:09:40,996
I'm not like you.

155
00:09:41,676 --> 00:09:42,957
Someone loves me.

156
00:09:43,717 --> 00:09:44,477
At least,

157
00:09:44,756 --> 00:09:46,317
Ruoxi loved me.

158
00:09:46,317 --> 00:09:47,837
You'll get what you deserve.

159
00:09:47,957 --> 00:09:48,996
You deserve it.

160
00:09:49,156 --> 00:09:50,237
- Pah!
- Su Yunian,

161
00:09:50,557 --> 00:09:51,437
calm down.

162
00:09:51,437 --> 00:09:52,516
Listen to me,

163
00:09:52,916 --> 00:09:53,916
from now on...

164
00:09:54,077 --> 00:09:54,916
Are you okay?

165
00:09:56,357 --> 00:09:57,077
Chu Bai.

166
00:10:08,437 --> 00:10:09,237
Chu Bai.

167
00:10:49,756 --> 00:10:50,557
Feng,

168
00:10:51,837 --> 00:10:52,756
we're both men.

169
00:10:52,756 --> 00:10:53,717
No more nonsense.

170
00:10:54,276 --> 00:10:54,916
Speak.

171
00:10:56,077 --> 00:10:57,276
What do you plan to do?

172
00:11:00,276 --> 00:11:02,796
That's more like it.

173
00:11:04,837 --> 00:11:05,916
Jiasheng,

174
00:11:06,957 --> 00:11:08,036
attitude

175
00:11:08,957 --> 00:11:10,477
matters a lot.

176
00:11:11,676 --> 00:11:12,876
I always say,

177
00:11:14,197 --> 00:11:15,317
my left hand

178
00:11:15,916 --> 00:11:17,876
can lift you up,

179
00:11:18,957 --> 00:11:20,557
but my right hand

180
00:11:23,156 --> 00:11:25,276
is even stronger.

181
00:11:27,077 --> 00:11:28,317
Come on,

182
00:11:29,077 --> 00:11:30,036
Jiasheng.

183
00:11:30,837 --> 00:11:31,957
Let me

184
00:11:32,077 --> 00:11:33,676
tell you my plan.

185
00:11:34,557 --> 00:11:36,276
But before that,

186
00:11:37,357 --> 00:11:38,957
let's first pay respects

187
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:40,756
to eldest brother.

188
00:11:41,756 --> 00:11:42,237
Let's go.

189
00:12:24,557 --> 00:12:25,957
That's right.

190
00:12:26,036 --> 00:12:27,557
Worship Liu Bei more.

191
00:12:27,557 --> 00:12:30,516
After all, he aimed for the world,

192
00:12:30,516 --> 00:12:33,344
while Guan Yu only guarded Jingzhou.

193
00:12:33,344 --> 00:12:34,208
Feng,

194
00:12:34,208 --> 00:12:35,680
I admire Guan Yu.

195
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,248
Then I'll have to make you

196
00:12:37,376 --> 00:12:39,232
hit the rough patch.

197
00:12:46,324 --> 00:12:49,998
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

198
00:12:50,297 --> 00:12:53,488
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

199
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:58,941
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

200
00:12:59,490 --> 00:13:02,289
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

201
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:07,490
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

202
00:13:07,714 --> 00:13:11,211
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

203
00:13:12,610 --> 00:13:16,297
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

204
00:13:16,935 --> 00:13:22,050
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

205
00:13:22,754 --> 00:13:26,888
♪I feel guilty♪

206
00:13:27,458 --> 00:13:31,202
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

207
00:13:32,066 --> 00:13:35,509
♪Even in tears♪

208
00:13:36,258 --> 00:13:40,172
♪It doesn't matter♪

209
00:13:40,354 --> 00:13:44,177
♪We embrace in dreams♪

210
00:13:45,026 --> 00:13:48,464
♪I let down all my defenses♪

211
00:13:49,698 --> 00:13:53,061
♪Though the story has its end♪

212
00:13:53,826 --> 00:14:02,178
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
